{"tid":1431922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔要大台！！！","createTime":"2019-08-08T05:59:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T12:54:11.000Z","uid":105795,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b67edd5e88d79c85c78d03e49ae913ac68e19ca3","tid":1431922,"uid":105795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:59:42.000Z","msg":"能夠持續2個月嘅最大原因就係「我地無大台」<br />\n「無大台」亦將會係我地繼續抗爭嘅最大後盾！<br />\n<br />\n出得嚟嘅手足都係基於個人意志而選擇企出嚟為公義發聲<br />\n兄弟爬山 尊重現場決定<br />\n核彈都唔撚割！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對家好清楚呢一點<br />\n所以佢地想吹風起大台<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我唔要大台！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"80a20754b153835e52e4e922730c7e513f19d74f","tid":1431922,"uid":231909,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:00:01.000Z","msg":"借個位,提提你<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BmepMAH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBmepMAH.jpg&h=aab03643&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xp7KMz5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxp7KMz5.png&h=1dddb453&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>出黎嬴翻香港</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"563f50b6d282ff2a95fc567476cefb60a2a6d71d","tid":1431922,"uid":105795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:00:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔要大台！</span></span>"},{"pid":"b5b78e83ef1085e597a164bec9f04afef0ca9859","tid":1431922,"uid":1965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:01:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f7be3cfe2c9b7ca12d8462bb2ede510a0dff6d1","tid":1431922,"uid":105795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:01:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-